{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_11_01",
  "title": "川咲さくら 1話 想いよ届け～！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です！　{user}さん！\n今度のCM撮影の詳細が届いたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work today‚ {user}-san!\nDid the details for the upcoming CM shoot arrive?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7566.6666667,
          "startTime": 11.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。今回のCMのテーマは『青春』らしい\nさくらには学生風の衣装を着てもらうことになるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. It seems the theme of this CM is “youth.”\nYou’ll be wearing a student-style outfit‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.2831066767
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "学校生活を送る姿を撮影して、最後にはチョコを\n渡しながら告白するシーンまであるんですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll film scenes of school life‚ and at the end‚\nthere’s even a scene where we confess while handing over chocolate!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.2001370429
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "告白かぁ……実はバレンタインイベントの方でも\nみんなで告白の実演をしようって話してるんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A confession‚ huh… Actually‚ for the Valentine’s event too‚\nwe’ve been talking about doing confession reenactments together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7000006358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "こういうイベントとしては鉄板のシチュエーションだな\n前にトリエルもCMで告白シーンを熱演していたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s a classic situation for this kind of event.\nTRINITYAiLE also gave a passionate confession scene in a CM before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 42.9731082279
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "コスプレしてファンにお菓子を手渡すイベントなんかも\nバレンタインでは定番ですよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cosplay events where you hand sweets to fans\nare a Valentine’s Day staple too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.187144788
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、トリエルも告白シーンを熱演したとなれば\n私も負けないくらい頑張らないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And if TRINITYAiLE did such a great confession scene‚\nthen I have to work just as hard!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.0081223169
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　告白シーン？　告白シーン……告白……\nわああ！？　私、告白なんてしたことありません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? A confession scene? Confession scene… confession…\nWaaah!? I’ve never confessed to anyone before!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "どうしましょう！？　私、演技のお仕事も経験が\n少ないのに、告白なんて上手に出来るでしょうか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I do!? I don’t even have much experience\nwith acting jobs—can I really pull off a confession!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.328189818
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "しっかり練習すれば、さくらならきっと大丈夫だ\n以前あった仕事でも、うまくこなしていただろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you practice properly‚ I’m sure you’ll be fine‚ Sakura.\nYou handled previous jobs well too‚ didn’t you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですね！　あの時みたいに沢山練習すれば\n私も魅力的な告白が出来るかもしれません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you’re right! If I practice a lot like back then‚\nI might be able to give a charming confession too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.2960583369
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "よーっし！　沢山勉強して、銀河一の告白を\nファンのみんなに届けてみせますよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright! I’ll study hard and deliver\nthe greatest confession in the galaxy to all my fans~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "銀河一というのはよく分からないが、やる気は十分だな\n俺も付き合うから、いつでも頼ってくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t quite get the “in the galaxy” part‚ but you’re motivated.\nI’ll help you too‚ so rely on me anytime.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.8962264378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\nじゃあ今度、告白の練習相手になって下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much!\nThen next time‚ please be my confession practice partner!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.5948659578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 124.7281855583
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "では！　勉強の成果を披露しますね！\n私の告白で、肉抜きにしちゃいますよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright! I’ll show you the results of my studying!\nMy confession will leave you meatless—!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それを言うなら骨抜きだと思うが……。でも、いろんな\n人に話を聞いて来たんだよな？　期待してるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think you mean “boneless”… But you did talk\nto a lot of people‚ right? I’m looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　今回のテーマに向き合って\nしっかり学んできました！　それでは、いきます……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I really faced this theme\nand learned properly! Here I go…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "うおおおおおおおおお！\nあなたのことが大好きでぇぇぇーっす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uooooooooh!\nI love you sooooo muuuch!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "うわっ！？　ス、ストップストップ！\nなぜ急にそんな大声を！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa!? S-stop‚ stop!\nWhy are you suddenly shouting like that!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "愛ちゃんに聞いたら、青春とはズバリ\n汗と涙が重要だと言ってたので！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I asked Ai-chan‚ and she said youth is\nall about sweat and tears!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.3333384196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "運動部みたいに、気合いを込めて伝えてみました！\nどうですか？　私の気持ちは届きましたか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I tried conveying it with sports-club spirit!\nHow was it? Did my feelings reach you!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.5333353678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "さくららしいが……少し勢いがあり過ぎかもな\nもっと雰囲気が出る感じを意識してみたらどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s very Sakura-like… but maybe a bit too intense.\nHow about focusing more on the atmosphere?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.3666717529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "雰囲気ですか……。あっ！　それならこの前\nすみれちゃんから教わりました！　やってみますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Atmosphere… Ah! In that case‚\nSumire-chan taught me something the other day! I’ll try it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.4333384196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr017.m4a",
      "text": "むむむ……！　むむむむむむ……！\n届け～！　想いよ届け～！　ビビビビビー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmm…! Mmmmmmm…!\nReach them! My feelings‚ reach them! Bibibibibi~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.2000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr018.m4a",
      "text": "……ふぅ。どうでしょうか？　言葉を使わずに\n気持ちを表現するんだよって教えてもらったんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Phew. How was that? She told me\nto express feelings without words!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.0666717529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "これもちょっと斬新過ぎるな……一旦勢いは\n抑えめにして、愛らしい感じにするのはどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is a bit too innovative too… Maybe dial\nback the energy and go for something sweet?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.5333384196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr019.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かりました！　愛ちゃんらしく、気合いを――\nじゃなくて！　可愛らしくですよね。可愛らしく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-okay! Like Ai-chan said‚ with sweat—\nI mean! Sweet‚ right. Sweet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 232.5000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_11_01-skr020.m4a",
      "text": "あなたのこトが……好き、デス……？\n私と付き合っテ、くーだサイ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I… li-like… you…?\nP-please… go~ out with me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 245.0000050862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
